WEBVTT

00:01:59.248 --> 00:02:01.056
How do we make sure

00:02:01.056 --> 00:02:02.636
that we have a great business

00:02:02.636 --> 00:02:05.508
but we also have a great environment around us?

00:02:05.508 --> 00:02:06.828
And that model

00:02:06.828 --> 00:02:09.797
is all about doing well and doing good.

00:02:09.797 --> 00:02:12.118
But the question is easier said than done.

00:02:12.118 --> 00:02:14.255
But how do we actually get that done?

00:02:14.255 --> 00:02:15.601
And I do believe

00:02:15.601 --> 00:02:18.691
that the answer to that is going to be leadership.

00:02:18.691 --> 00:02:20.048
It is going to be to redefine

00:02:20.048 --> 00:02:21.918
the new business models

00:02:21.918 --> 00:02:23.264
which understand

00:02:23.264 --> 00:02:25.269
that the only license to operate

00:02:25.269 --> 00:02:27.406
is to combine these things.

00:02:27.406 --> 00:02:29.338
And for that you need businesses

00:02:29.338 --> 00:02:32.097
that can actually define their role